{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.009.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. Ps 40:7-9. H\u00e9 9:7-15, 23-28.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>En effet, la loi, qui poss\u00e8de une ombre des biens \u00e0 venir, et non l\u2019exacte repr\u00e9sentation des choses, ne peut jamais, par les m\u00eames sacrifices qu\u2019on offre perp\u00e9tuellement chaque ann\u00e9e, amener les assistants \u00e0 la perfection.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.9.28","name":"H\u00e9breux 9:28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.9.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Autrement, n\u2019aurait-on pas cess\u00e9 de les offrir, parce que ceux qui rendent ce culte, \u00e9tant une fois purifi\u00e9s, n\u2019auraient plus eu aucune conscience de leurs p\u00e9ch\u00e9s?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mais le souvenir des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s est renouvel\u00e9 chaque ann\u00e9e par ces sacrifices;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>car il est impossible que le sang des taureaux et des boucs \u00f4te les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi Christ, entrant dans le monde, dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Tu n\u2019as voulu ni sacrifice ni offrande,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">mais tu m\u2019as form\u00e9 un corps;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>tu n\u2019as agr\u00e9\u00e9 ni holocaustes ni sacrifices pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Alors j\u2019ai dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">voici, je viens<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">(Dans le rouleau du livre il est question de moi)<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">pour faire, \u00f4 Dieu, ta volont\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir dit d\u2019abord:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu n\u2019as voulu et tu n\u2019as agr\u00e9\u00e9 ni sacrifices ni offrandes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">ni holocaustes ni sacrifices pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">(ce qu\u2019on offre selon la loi),<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>il dit ensuite:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Voici, je viens<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">pour faire ta volont\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">Il abolit ainsi la premi\u00e8re chose pour \u00e9tablir la seconde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>C\u2019est en vertu de cette volont\u00e9 que nous sommes sanctifi\u00e9s, par l\u2019offrande du corps de J\u00e9sus-Christ, une fois pour toutes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et tandis que tout sacrificateur fait chaque jour le service et offre souvent les m\u00eames sacrifices, qui ne peuvent jamais \u00f4ter les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>lui, apr\u00e8s avoir offert un seul sacrifice pour les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, s\u2019est assis pour toujours \u00e0 la droite de Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>attendant d\u00e9sormais que ses ennemis soient devenus son marchepied.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car, par une seule offrande, il a amen\u00e9 \u00e0 la perfection pour toujours ceux qui sont sanctifi\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.15","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:15","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>C\u2019est ce que le Saint-Esprit nous atteste aussi; car, apr\u00e8s avoir dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.16","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:16","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Voici l\u2019alliance que je ferai avec eux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">apr\u00e8s ces jours-l\u00e0, dit le Seigneur:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je mettrai mes lois dans leurs c\u0153urs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">et je les \u00e9crirai dans leur esprit,<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">il ajoute:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.17","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:17","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et je ne me souviendrai plus de leurs p\u00e9ch\u00e9s ni de leurs iniquit\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.18","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:18","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Or, l\u00e0 o\u00f9 il y a pardon des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s, il n\u2019y a plus d\u2019offrande pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.19","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:19","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.020,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la confiance et \u00e0 la fermet\u00e9 dans la foi<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 19-31: cf. (Jn 14:6. \u00c9p 2:13, 18. H\u00e9 4:14-16.) (H\u00e9 3:12-14; 6:4-8; 12:25-29.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Ainsi donc, fr\u00e8res, puisque nous avons, au moyen du sang de J\u00e9sus, une libre entr\u00e9e dans le sanctuaire<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.20","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:20","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>par la route nouvelle et vivante qu\u2019il a inaugur\u00e9e pour nous au travers du voile, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire, de sa chair,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.21","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:21","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>et puisque nous avons un souverain sacrificateur \u00e9tabli sur la maison de Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.20","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:20","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.22","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:22","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>approchons-nous avec un c\u0153ur sinc\u00e8re, dans la pl\u00e9nitude de la foi, les c\u0153urs purifi\u00e9s d\u2019une mauvaise conscience, et le corps lav\u00e9 d\u2019une eau pure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.21","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:21","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.23","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:23","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Retenons fermement la profession de notre esp\u00e9rance, car celui qui a fait la promesse est fid\u00e8le.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.22","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:22","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.24","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:24","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Veillons les uns sur les autres, pour nous exciter \u00e0 la charit\u00e9 et aux bonnes \u0153uvres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.23","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:23","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.25","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:25","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>N\u2019abandonnons pas notre assembl\u00e9e, comme c\u2019est la coutume de quelques-uns; mais exhortons-nous r\u00e9ciproquement, et cela d\u2019autant plus que vous voyez s\u2019approcher le jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.24","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:24","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.26","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:26","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Car, si nous p\u00e9chons volontairement apr\u00e8s avoir re\u00e7u la connaissance de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il ne reste plus de sacrifice pour les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.25","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:25","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.27","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:27","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>mais une attente terrible du jugement et l\u2019ardeur d\u2019un feu qui d\u00e9vorera les rebelles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.28","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.26","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:26","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.28","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:28","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Celui qui a viol\u00e9 la loi de Mo\u00efse meurt sans mis\u00e9ricorde, sur la d\u00e9position de deux ou de trois t\u00e9moins;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.29","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.27","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:27","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.29","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:29","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>de quel pire ch\u00e2timent pensez-vous que sera jug\u00e9 digne celui qui aura foul\u00e9 aux pieds le Fils de Dieu, qui aura tenu pour profane le sang de l\u2019alliance, par lequel il a \u00e9t\u00e9 sanctifi\u00e9, et qui aura outrag\u00e9 l\u2019Esprit de la gr\u00e2ce?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.30","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.28","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:28","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.30","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:30","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Car nous connaissons celui qui a dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    A moi la vengeance, \u00e0 moi la r\u00e9tribution!<\/p>\n<p class=\"m\">et encore:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Le Seigneur jugera son peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.31","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.29","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:29","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.31","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:31","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>C\u2019est une chose terrible que de tomber entre les mains du Dieu vivant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.32","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.30","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:30","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.32","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:32","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-39: cf. H\u00e9 6:9-20. Ga 3:4. Mc 13:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Souvenez-vous de ces premiers jours, o\u00f9, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e9clair\u00e9s, vous avez soutenu un grand combat au milieu des souffrances,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.33","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.31","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:31","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.33","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:33","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>d\u2019une part, expos\u00e9s comme en spectacle aux opprobres et aux tribulations, et de l\u2019autre, vous associant \u00e0 ceux dont la position \u00e9tait la m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.34","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.32","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:32","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.34","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:34","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>En effet, vous avez eu de la compassion pour les prisonniers, et vous avez accept\u00e9 avec joie l\u2019enl\u00e8vement de vos biens, sachant que vous avez des biens meilleurs et qui durent toujours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.35","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.33","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:33","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.35","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:35","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>N\u2019abandonnez donc pas votre assurance, \u00e0 laquelle est attach\u00e9e une grande r\u00e9mun\u00e9ration.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.36","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.34","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:34","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.36","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:36","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Car vous avez besoin de pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance, afin qu\u2019apr\u00e8s avoir accompli la volont\u00e9 de Dieu, vous obteniez ce qui vous est promis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.37","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.35","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:35","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.37","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:37","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Encore un peu, un peu de temps: celui qui doit venir viendra, et il ne tardera pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.38","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.36","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:36","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.38","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:38","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.010.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Et mon juste vivra par la foi; mais, s\u2019il se retire, mon \u00e2me ne prend pas plaisir en lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.39","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:39","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.37","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:37","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.39","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 10:39","prev_osis_id":"Heb.010.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.10.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Nous, nous ne sommes pas de ceux qui se retirent pour se perdre, mais de ceux qui ont la foi pour sauver leur \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.11.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.10.38","name":"H\u00e9breux 10:38","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.10.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5de5382.17552130');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5de5382.17552130\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5de5382.17552130","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb5de5382.17552130'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5de5382.17552130\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}